          <declname>uvc_dev</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Withdraw the configuration of an UVC device instance. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Reset the configuration of an USB device class, make it ready to be enabled again.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>uvc_dev</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to the UVC device to deconfigure </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 on success, negative value on error </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
